{
  "text": "Let's walk through a simple Pulumi example. We import the AWS library. We create a VPC using the new keyword. We set the CIDR block to 10.0.0.0.0/.16. We enable DNS hostnames and DNS support. We add organizational tags like name and environment. And finally, we export the VPC ID so it can be consumed by other stacks.",
